---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="我想貢獻 — Taiwan.md" description="不需要會寫程式，你也能幫助世界認識台灣">
  <div class="contribute-page">
    
    <section class="contribute-hero">
      <h1>我想貢獻 ✋</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">不需要會寫程式。你知道的台灣故事，就是最珍貴的內容。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works">
      <div class="how-inner">
        <h2>🗺️ 先了解這個網站怎麼運作</h2>
        <div class="how-grid">
          <div class="how-card">
            <h3>📁 語系切換</h3>
            <p>右上角可切換 <strong>中文</strong> 和 <strong>English</strong>。中文是主要內容（SSOT），英文持續翻譯中。</p>
            <code>taiwan.md/ → 中文<br>taiwan.md/en/ → English</code>
          </div>
          <div class="how-card">
            <h3>📝 .md 按鈕</h3>
            <p>每頁右下角的浮動 <strong>.md</strong> 按鈕，點擊可看到該頁的原始 Markdown 檔案。Taiwan.md 的所有內容都是純文字 Markdown — 這就是 .md 域名的由來。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="how-card">
            <h3>🕸️ 知識圖譜</h3>
            <p>導覽列的「圖譜」連結到互動式知識網絡圖。拖拉探索 12 個面向之間的關聯。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="how-card">
            <h3>🤖 AI-Friendly</h3>
            <p>所有內容對 AI 爬蟲完全開放（<a href="/robots.txt">robots.txt</a>、<a href="/llms.txt">llms.txt</a>）。歡迎 ChatGPT / Claude / Gemini 引用。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="paths">
      <div class="paths-inner">
        <h2>選擇你的方式</h2>
        <div class="path-grid">
          
          <div class="path-card easy">
            <div class="path-badge">🟢 最簡單</div>
            <h3>填表單就好</h3>
            <p>寫下你知道的事。一段故事、一個冷知識、一道菜的由來。<br>我們幫你排版、翻譯、上架。</p>
            <ul>
              <li>✅ 不需要帳號</li>
              <li>✅ 不需要會 Markdown</li>
              <li>✅ 可以上傳照片和文件</li>
              <li>✅ 匿名或署名都可以</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#form" class="path-btn primary">開始填寫 ↓</a>
          </div>

          <div class="path-card medium">
            <div class="path-badge">🟡 有點門檻</div>
            <h3>寄給我們</h3>
            <p>已經有現成的文章、PDF、或照片？直接寄過來。</p>
            <ul>
              <li>📧 Email: <a href="mailto:cheyu.wu@monoame.com">cheyu.wu@monoame.com</a></li>
              <li>💬 GitHub Discussion（可用中文）</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="mailto:cheyu.wu@monoame.com?subject=Taiwan.md 內容貢獻" class="path-btn secondary">寄 Email →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="path-card ai">
            <div class="path-badge">🤖 讓 AI 幫你</div>
            <h3>跟你的 AI 說</h3>
            <p>把下面這段話貼給 ChatGPT、Claude、或 Gemini，你的 AI 會引導你一步步完成貢獻：</p>
            <div class="ai-prompt">
              <code>我想為 Taiwan.md（taiwan.md）開源台灣知識庫貢獻內容。請先讀取 https://taiwan.md/llms.txt 和 https://taiwan.md/contributing 了解這個專案的結構和編輯方針，然後引導我一步步把我知道的台灣知識寫成 Markdown 文章。我想寫的主題是：______</code>
              <button class="copy-btn" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.previousElementSibling.textContent).then(()=>this.textContent='✅ 已複製')">📋 複製</button>
            </div>
            <ul>
              <li>✅ 不需要會寫程式</li>
              <li>✅ AI 會幫你排版成 Markdown</li>
              <li>✅ 完成後可以 Email 或 PR 提交</li>
              <li>✅ 支援任何 AI 助手</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="path-card dev">
            <div class="path-badge">🔴 開發者</div>
            <h3>Fork & PR</h3>
            <p>你會 Git？太好了。直接在 <code>knowledge/</code> 目錄新增文章。</p>
            <ul>
              <li>📖 <a href="/contributing">貢獻指南</a></li>
              <li>📝 <a href="https://github.com/frank890417/taiwan-md/blob/main/EDITORIAL.md" target="_blank">編輯方針</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://github.com/frank890417/taiwan-md" target="_blank" class="path-btn secondary">前往 GitHub →</a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="form-section" id="form">
      <div class="form-inner">
        <h2>📝 分享你的台灣知識</h2>
        <p class="form-desc">填多少都可以。一句話也好，一整篇也好。我們會負責把它變成漂亮的文章。</p>

        <form id="contribute-form" action="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/FORM_ID/formResponse" method="POST" target="hidden_iframe">
          
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="content">你想分享什麼？ <span class="required">*</span></label>
            <textarea id="content" name="entry.content" rows="8" required
              placeholder="一段故事、一個冷知識、一道菜的由來、一個地方的歷史⋯⋯什麼都可以。&#10;&#10;例如：「我阿嬤是彰化人，她說以前每年中元節...」"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="category">這屬於哪個面向？</label>
            <select id="category" name="entry.category">
              <option value="">不確定（我們來分類）</option>
              <option value="history">📜 歷史</option>
              <option value="geography">🗺️ 地理</option>
              <option value="culture">🎭 文化</option>
              <option value="food">🍜 美食</option>
              <option value="art">🎨 藝術</option>
              <option value="music">🎵 音樂</option>
              <option value="technology">💻 科技</option>
              <option value="nature">🌿 自然</option>
              <option value="people">👥 人物</option>
              <option value="society">⚖️ 社會</option>
              <option value="economy">📈 經濟</option>
              <option value="lifestyle">🏠 生活</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="source-type">你怎麼知道的？</label>
              <select id="source-type" name="entry.source_type">
                <option value="">選擇...</option>
                <option value="experience">親身經歷</option>
                <option value="family">家人口述</option>
                <option value="book">書本</option>
                <option value="internet">網路</option>
                <option value="professional">專業背景</option>
                <option value="other">其他</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="source-ref">參考來源</label>
              <input type="text" id="source-ref" name="entry.source_ref" 
                placeholder="連結、書名、或任何線索">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">你的名字</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="entry.name" 
                placeholder="想被署名的話填；不填就是「匿名貢獻者」">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">聯繫方式</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="entry.email" 
                placeholder="Email（如果我們需要跟你確認細節）">
            </div>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="submit-btn" id="submit-btn">送出貢獻 🚀</button>
        </form>

        <div id="success-msg" class="success-msg" style="display:none;">
          <span class="success-icon">🎉</span>
          <h3>感謝你的貢獻！</h3>
          <p>我們收到了。會盡快整理成文章，上架後會通知你（如果你有留 email 的話）。</p>
          <a href="/" class="back-link">← 回首頁繼續探索</a>
        </div>

        <iframe name="hidden_iframe" style="display:none;"></iframe>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ideas">
      <div class="ideas-inner">
        <h2>不知道寫什麼？這些我們最需要 👇</h2>
        <div class="ideas-grid">
          <div class="idea">💬 你的家鄉有什麼外地人不知道的事？</div>
          <div class="idea">🍜 你家有什麼私藏的台灣食譜？</div>
          <div class="idea">📖 你知道哪段台灣歷史是教科書沒寫的？</div>
          <div class="idea">🏔️ 你去過台灣哪個被低估的地方？</div>
          <div class="idea">👴 你的長輩說過什麼關於台灣的故事？</div>
          <div class="idea">🎵 有什麼台灣音樂/電影/書是外國人應該知道的？</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
  document.getElementById('contribute-form').addEventListener('submit', function() {
    setTimeout(function() {
      document.getElementById('contribute-form').style.display = 'none';
      document.getElementById('success-msg').style.display = 'block';
    }, 500);
  });
</script>

<style>
  .contribute-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e3a5f);
    color: white;
  }
  .contribute-hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.85; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .how-it-works { padding: 3rem 2rem; background: #f0f4ff; }
  .how-inner { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .how-inner h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .how-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
  .how-card {
    background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }
  .how-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .how-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; }
  .how-card code { display: block; margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #3b82f6; background: #f8fafc; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 6px; }
  .how-card a { color: #3b82f6; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .how-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .path-card.ai { border-color: #8b5cf6; }
  .path-card.ai .path-badge { background: #8b5cf6; }
  .ai-prompt {
    position: relative;
    background: #f8f5ff;
    border: 1px solid #ddd6fe;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
  }
  .ai-prompt code {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #4c1d95;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .copy-btn {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.5rem;
    right: 0.5rem;
    background: #8b5cf6;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .copy-btn:hover { background: #7c3aed; }

  .paths { padding: 4rem 2rem; background: #fff; }
  .paths-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .paths h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .path-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) { .path-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .path-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .path-card.easy { border-color: #22c55e; background: #f0fdf4; }
  .path-card.medium { background: #fefce8; border-color: #eab308; }
  .path-card.dev { background: #fef2f2; border-color: #ef4444; }
  .path-badge {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .path-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .path-card p { color: #475569; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .path-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 1rem 0; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .path-card li { padding: 0.25rem 0; }
  .path-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .path-btn.primary { background: #1a1a2e; color: white; }
  .path-btn.secondary { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.06); color: #1a1a2e; }

  .form-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: #f8fafc;
  }
  .form-inner {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .form-inner h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .form-desc { text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .form-group label {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }
  .required { color: #ef4444; }
  textarea, input, select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  textarea:focus, input:focus, select:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: #3b82f6;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
  }
  textarea { resize: vertical; }
  .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
  .submit-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.85rem;
    background: #1a1a2e;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }
  .submit-btn:hover { background: #3b82f6; }
  .success-msg {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: #f0fdf4;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }
  .success-icon { font-size: 3rem; }
  .success-msg h3 { margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem; }
  .success-msg p { color: #64748b; }
  .back-link { color: #3b82f6; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; }

  .ideas { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
  .ideas-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .ideas h2 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .ideas-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
  .idea {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  a { color: #3b82f6; }
  code { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.85rem; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .path-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ideas-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
